{"tid":754531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥總統當選人AMLO授權未來政府研究毒品合法化","createTime":"2018-07-24T12:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T07:18:00.000Z","uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc6490ccb54be01b37fdf4759e2245b74352304a","tid":754531,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%8E%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-105003802.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%2593%25A5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25A8%258E%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E6%2580%25A7-105003802.html&d=fc7yIvJIluIa%2FFMUpegtYS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=411913ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A2%A8%E8%A5%BF%E5%93%A5%E6%96%B0%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A2%E8%A8%8E%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%80%A7-105003802.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（法新社墨西哥市17日電） 墨西哥總統當選人羅培茲歐布拉多（Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador）已經「全權賦予」未來的內政部長，將探討毒品合法可能性，以遏制國內暴力犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n即將接任內政部長的柯戴羅（Sanchez Cordero）表示：「關於毒品合法化的議題，總統有跟我說，我引述為：『全權賦予』。無論這個國家需要什麼來恢復和平，就讓我們展開討論吧。」<br />\n<br />\n曾擔任最高法院法官的柯戴羅還指出，她計畫在國會提出「過渡司法系統」法案。羅培茲歐布拉多所屬國家復興運動黨（Morena）帶領的聯盟於參、眾兩院取得絕對多數席次。<br />\n<br />\n法案內容包括減少罪犯的刑期，若他們提供尚未偵破的犯罪案件線索，例如數以萬計的墨西哥民眾失蹤案件；還有成立類似用於衝突後局勢的真相委員會、特別調查委員會，以及被害者的賠償方案。<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥政府從2006年部署軍隊打擊毒品交易以來，國家就一直陷入暴力動盪，至今發生逾20萬件謀殺案。<br />\n<br />\n柯戴羅說：「墨西哥成立過渡司法系統是可能且急迫的，這不僅限於暴力受害者，且適用墨西哥社會的所有人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.l4yYv2RXMzlmzc_zBoXlA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDE5/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/afp.cnanews.gov.tw/d23448f21a8dd7407ac63bca892d0d27\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.l4yYv2RXMzlmzc_zBoXlA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDE5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fafp.cnanews.gov.tw%2Fd23448f21a8dd7407ac63bca892d0d27&h=f02971ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ca3f796dc49dbe49a068f5f41da41aa734c162a","tid":754531,"uid":62532,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"不如宣報殺人合法<br />\n<br />\n謀殺案直接變0<br />\n<br />\n做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e4beb3ddeb6a8a96045f8c68bcc51c09f7db1a","tid":754531,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ca3f796dc49dbe49a068f5f41da41aa734c162a","tid":754531,"uid":62532,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"不如宣報殺人合法<br />\n<br />\n謀殺案直接變0<br />\n<br />\n做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"墨西哥毒梟收入主要源於出口美國, 如果毒品合法呢樣就變美國自己邊防問題<br />\n同埋合法化後班cartels繼續打仗嘅成本就會上升, 反而有助緩和暴力, 而家墨西哥係打緊內戰"},{"pid":"3cf08658b4edb7039634553ab8bd8813aaf981d2","tid":754531,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1b90a706914f4a3acdfc495176ec3dcfa17a0d","tid":754531,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"中共政府研究 毒奶粉 毒疫苗 合法化<br />\n<br />\n以後不存在 毒奶粉 毒疫苗 問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6783e7cdce39b450ab3f247950fcb9983d32e09e","tid":754531,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e1b90a706914f4a3acdfc49